</tr>
<tr>
<td>Scope</td>
<td>Global, all languages, all topics</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Target</td>
<td>Content quality assessment</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Recovery time</td>
<td>Weeks to months</td>
</tr>
<tr>
<td>Announcement</td>
<td>Google confirms major updates</td>
</tr>
</tbody>
</table></div>
<p><strong>How core updates differ from other updates:</strong></p>
<div class="table-wrap"><table>
<thead>
<tr>
<th>Update Type</th>
<th>What It Targets</th>
<th>Recovery Approach</th>
</tr>
</thead>
